title: Traded no longer available EPDG Powell SGC40
author: RayBShotz

posts.post_title: Traded no longer available EPDG Powell SGC40
posts.post_content:
I've kicked off my 3rd T206 journey with the PSA Set Registry and thought when I bought this card I would cross it. With the extensive grading delays, I will no longer have the patience to wait.
So, despite this card being perhaps the nicest one I own, I'm parting with it.

Edited to add its been TRADED. Trade for a PSA graded T206 of equal, lesser or greater value with cash or additional cards making up the difference.
RayB

Sorry Shawn - The card had been previously Traded.
RayB
